msgid "Redemption amount - allows the issuer to limit the amount of RTokens redeemed per hour. This matters in the event of an exploit where an attacker tries to redeem RTokens.This buys time for users with pause or freeze permissions to reduce the amount of RTokens that can be redeemed."
