msgid "Welcome to Reserve — a platform for creating, exploring, and interacting with Decentralized Token Funds (“DTFs”). A DTF is the generic name given to any onchain asset-backed index. DTFs can be created on Reserve’s Yield Protocol or Index Protocol permissionlessly, by any person or entity."
